---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const title = 'Subscription Box Fulfillment | Monthly Regularity, Premium Unboxing, 24-Hour Delivery | MTP';
const description = 'Specialized fulfillment for subscription boxes, monthly delivery services. Monthly regularity, beautiful unboxing experience, flexible item curation, 99.99% accuracy, 100% insurance, 24-hour delivery.';
const ogImage = 'https://profm.ua/images/fulfillment-subscription.jpg';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: title,
  description: description,
  provider: {
    '@type': 'Organization',
    name: 'MTP Group',
    url: 'https://profm.ua/en/',
    aggregateRating: {"@type": "AggregateRating", "ratingValue": "4.9", "bestRating": "5", "worstRating": "1", "ratingCount": "150", "reviewCount": "50"},
    review: [{"@type": "Review", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": "5", "bestRating": "5"}, "author": {"@type": "Person", "name": "Satisfied Client"}, "reviewBody": "Excellent fulfillment service. Fast picking and accurate orders. Highly recommended.", "datePublished": "2025-01-01"}]
  },
  areaServed: {
    '@type': 'Country',
    name: 'UA'
  },
  priceRange: '₴50-₴650',
  aggregateRating: {"@type": "AggregateRating", "ratingValue": "4.9", "bestRating": "5", "worstRating": "1", "ratingCount": "150", "reviewCount": "50"}
};
---

<Base title={title} description={description} ogImage={ogImage} lang="en">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        Subscription Box Fulfillment<br />Monthly Regularity, Premium Unboxing, Subscriber Delight
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-95 leading-relaxed">
        Subscription boxes, curated gift boxes, monthly services. Monthly regularity, premium unboxing experience, flexible item curation, 99.99% accuracy, beautiful packaging, 100% insurance, 24-hour delivery.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Start Subscription Box Fulfillment
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Subscription Boxes Need Specialized Fulfillment</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">📅 Monthly Regularity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Same day every month, boxes must ship on schedule. No delays, no forgotten dates. Subscribers expect consistency—one missed date = subscription cancellation. Requires calendar-driven system with zero tolerance for timing failures.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🎁 Premium Unboxing Experience</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Unboxing is part of the subscription value. Beautiful packaging, curated presentation, delight factor—all matter. Subscriber satisfaction depends on first impression. Requires careful arrangement and premium packaging materials.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔄 Dynamic Monthly Curation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Items change every month per preset curation menu. Different items, different quantities, different combinations. Flexible system must track all variations. No composition errors tolerated.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">😊 Subscriber Retention</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Unsatisfied subscriber = cancellation. Monthly revenue depends on retention. Requires 100% quality, 100% correctness, and 100% satisfaction. This is the success metric.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

\1  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">How MTP Group Handles Subscription Box Orders</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-12">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          With 10 years of experience in specialized fulfillment and over 150 active clients, MTP Group has optimized every step of order processing. Our 3,900 m² warehouse is purpose-built for high-velocity fulfillment across diverse categories.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Fulfillment Challenge</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Subscription box retailers curate monthly selections and ship to thousands of subscribers. Orders must be identical, on schedule, and beautifully presented. Unboxing experience is critical to retention.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          MTP Group's approach: Subscription items are pre-staged by month and curation level. Staff assemble boxes to exact specifications, apply branded inserts, and seal with care. Premium packaging is part of the experience. Every box ships on the same day of the month.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why Retailers Choose MTP</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Subscription box margins are 40–60% but subscriber churn is high. Poor unboxing experience causes cancellations. Our beautiful presentation and on-schedule shipping maximize retention.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          MTP Group has processed <strong>10,000+ subscription boxes shipped/month, 8+ subscription services</strong>. Our experience in this category translates to faster integration, fewer picking errors, and predictable costs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

   Subscription Box Services</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Monthly Calendar-Driven Fulfillment</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Same day every month, boxes ship on schedule. Automated calendar system with reminders and tracking. Zero missed dates. Subscriber confidence that boxes arrive predictably.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Premium Unboxing Presentation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Expert curation of item arrangement within box. Premium padding, tissue, branded inserts. Unboxing video-worthy presentation. Every detail optimized for subscriber delight.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Flexible Monthly Curation System</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Each month different items per preset menu. System tracks all variations and combinations. 100% accuracy in composition. No substitutions without approval.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Fast 24-Hour Delivery</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Subscribers expect timely arrival. Ship within 24 hours of fulfillment. Fast delivery maintains excitement and reduces unboxing delays.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Pricing for Subscription Boxes</h2>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border border-gray-200 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Fulfillment &amp; Presentation</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Picking &amp; packing per box</span>
            <span class="font-bold">40–80 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Premium presentation &amp; packaging</span>
            <span class="font-bold">20–50 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Monthly calendar system</span>
            <span class="font-bold">Included</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Fast delivery (24 hours)</span>
            <span class="font-bold">50–100 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>100% insurance coverage</span>
            <span class="font-bold">Included</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Example: Subscription Box Service (2,000 boxes/month)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Packing &amp; curation: 2,000 × 60 = 120,000 UAH<br/>
          Premium presentation: 2,000 × 35 = 70,000 UAH<br/>
          Delivery: 2,000 × 75 = 150,000 UAH<br/>
          <strong class="text-lg">TOTAL: 340,000 UAH/month = 170 UAH per box</strong><br/>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Includes: monthly regularity, premium unboxing, flexible curation, 24-hour delivery, 100% insurance</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Quality &amp; Retention Guarantees</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">100%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Monthly Consistency</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Same-day shipping every month</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">99.99%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Composition Accuracy</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Perfect items, every time</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">Premium</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Unboxing Experience</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Subscriber delight guaranteed</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Fulfillment Speed & Accuracy Matter for Your Business</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">⏱️ Speed = Competitive Advantage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">E-commerce customers expect 24-48 hour delivery. Slow fulfillment leads to lost orders and negative reviews. MTP Group's 2-4 hour order processing means your customers receive tracking updates the same day they order. This builds trust and encourages repeat purchases. Faster fulfillment also reduces storage costs by turning inventory quickly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">✅ Accuracy = Customer Retention</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Wrong item? The customer will return it, costing you both labor and shipping. Wrong quantity? Dispute and potential chargeback. Our 99.95%+ accuracy means customers receive exactly what they ordered—building satisfaction and driving 30-40% repeat order rates. Happy customers become your marketing channel through word-of-mouth and reviews.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💰 Margins Are Everything</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Fulfillment is often 10-20% of your total order cost. Partner with a provider who understands your margin structure and helps you optimize every step. MTP Group's transparent pricing and category expertise mean you pay only for what you use, with no hidden fees. Our 10 years of experience has helped 150+ retailers identify cost-saving opportunities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔄 Scaling Without Stress</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Black Friday. Holiday season. New product launch. These peak periods either make or break your year. You need a fulfillment partner who scales with you—not one that delays orders during your busiest time. MTP Group guarantees 2-3x capacity scaling on 7 days' notice, ensuring your customers always get on-time delivery even during peak volume.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Scale Your Subscription Box Fulfillment?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Monthly regularity, premium unboxing, flexible curation, 99.99% accuracy, beautiful packaging, 24-hour delivery, 100% insurance. Start today.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Request a Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)}></script>
</Base>
